data.description: Cute home in Twin Lakes used primarily for weekends but would make great starter of retirement home. 2 bedroom, 1 Full Bath plus additional separate studio/3rd bedroom wit half bath on upper level. Neat and clean interior. Set on corner lot with 3/4 of an acre to garden and play. Within short distance to sparkling spring fed lake.
